	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Gnolls give faction to qey guards/merchants.  The guards will kill you if you have a bad faction.  Why do you think dark elves/ogres/trolls practically beg and pay heavily for invis/teleports when traveling?<BR>
<BR>
Specializing in evocation is great if you are totally into grouping for xp and you HAVE to play the wizard.  The bulk of the mage spells are conjuration.  If you solo for xp(like I do) spending less time medding after bringing out pet, food, water, weapons, armor, selling summoned goods etc. is more important than spending less time medding after battle IF I heavily used the evo line of damage spells.  There is a decent line of damage spells in conjuration.<BR>
<BR>
The power of the gatecallers is summoning.  Summoning = conjuration my friend.<BR>
<BR>
Haquiem 32nd Mage<BR>
Wandering Mage
				</font>
