				You should also consider the benefit of specializing in Evocation vs Conjugation.  You tend to summon things prior to combat so the specialization does not really help your summoning. You have time to regain mana prior to combat.  While some DD spells are conj based most of them are evo based.  The benefits of specialization really come in combat.  So an alternative to specializing in conj should be specializing in evo
